nodes.text: A mayor was a government official who served as a city's chief executive. Shaketown, a city on the planet Gorse, had a mayor, and the human Cobb Vanth served as the de facto mayor of Freetown, a city on Tatooine. The Mon Calamari Raddus served as the mayor of the Mon Cala city Nystullum before joining the Alliance to Restore the Republic.
